From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: HZHY Device Tree Port <dev@hzhy.com>
Date: Sat, 05 Jul 2026 00:00:00 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] ARM: dts: rockchip: Makefile: add HZHY MiniEVM SP DTS

Add the HZ-RK3506SP MiniEVM EMMC/NAND board device trees to the build, drop TF variant.
Signed-off-by: HZHY Device Tree Port <dev@hzhy.com>
---
 arch/arm/boot/dts/rockchip/Makefile | 2 ++
 1 file changed, 2 insertions(+)

diff --git a/arch/arm/boot/dts/rockchip/Makefile b/arch/arm/boot/dts/rockchip/Makefile
--- a/arch/arm/boot/dts/rockchip/Makefile
+++ b/arch/arm/boot/dts/rockchip/Makefile
@@ -46,3 +46,5 @@
 	rk3288-veyron-tiger.dtb \
 	rk3288-vyasa.dtb \
 	rk3506b-aes.dtb \
+	HZ-RK3506SP_MiniEVM_EMMC.dtb \
+	HZ-RK3506SP_MiniEVM_NAND.dtb
